{{Infobox journal | title = Universum | cover = | language = Spanish | discipline = [[Social science]], [[humanities]] | abbreviation = Universum | editor = Francisco Javier Pinedo | publisher = Instituto de Estudios Humanísticos Abate Juan Ignacio Molina [[University of Talca]] | country = Chile | frequency = Biannual | history = 1986-present | impact = | impact-year = | website = http://universum.utalca.cl/index.html | link1 = | link1-name = | ISSN = 0716-498X | eISSN = 0718-2376 | OCLC = 62074811 | LCCN = sf94090108 }} '''''Universum''''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] specialising in [[social science]]s and [[humanities]] of [[Latin America]]. It is published by the Instituto de Estudios Humanísticos Abate Juan Ignacio Molina ([[University of Talca]]) and is also financed by that university with the sponsorship of local companies. The [[editor-in-chief]] is Francisco Javier Pinedo (University of Talca).
